<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">ع:</span> مأخوذ من <span style="color:#950000">"الكَثَبَ"</span>، وهو القُرْب <span style="color:#008000">(١)</span> <span style="color:#008000">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
